Tributes are pouring in for actress Candy Moloi, who died on Tuesday. JOHANNESBURG - Tributes are pouring in for actress Candy Moloi, who died on Tuesday. She was known for her role as Vho-Makhadzi on popular soapie Muvhango. Moloi also acted on shows like Death of a Queen and Ring of Lies. READ: Veteran actress Mary Twala dies at 80 She's the mother of actress Lerato Moloi who just recovered from COVID-19. The cause of her death is currently unknown.